{
  "texts": [
    "The summary of our results comparing the GPT-based models against the SOTA models on three tasks are reported in Supplementary Table 1.",
    "Understanding the calibration of LLMs in text classification.",
    "In addition to the accuracy, we investigated the reliability of our GPT-based models and the SOTA models in terms of calibration.",
    "The reliability can be evaluated by measuring the expected calibration error (ECE) score 43 with 10 bins.",
    "A lower ECE score indicates that the model's predictions are closer to being well-calibrated, ensuring that the confidence of a model in its prediction is similar to the actual accuracy of the model 44, 45 (Refer to Methods section)."
  ]
}